  STklos 0.98            -> /Users/feeley/schemes/sys/stklos/bin/stklos

Please set your PATH like this (in your ~/.profile for example):

export PATH="/Users/feeley/schemes/sys/bigloo/bin:/Users/feeley/schemes/sys/chicken/bin:/Users/feeley/schemes/sys/gambit/bin:/Users/feeley/schemes/sys/gauche/bin:/Users/feeley/schemes/sys/kawa/bin:/Users/feeley/schemes/sys/larceny/larceny-0.97b1-bin-native-ia32-macosx:/Users/feeley/schemes/sys/mit/bin:/Users/feeley/schemes/sys/mzscheme/bin:/Users/feeley/schemes/sys/scheme48/bin:/Users/feeley/schemes/sys/scm/scm:/Users/feeley/schemes/sys/scsh/bin:/Users/feeley/schemes/sys/sisc/sisc-1.16.6:/Users/feeley/schemes/sys/stalin/stalin-0.11:/Users/feeley/schemes/sys/stklos/bin:$PATH"
